Instructions.
1. Clone the file contents to your folder
2. Install MySQL Server( https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/installer/ ) and execute the following commands on MySQL shell.
    create database ps5_login_info
    create table accounts( id int(255) primary key auto_increment, name varchar(10), age int(3), location varchar(10), password varchar(10));
3. On command prompt(run as admin) , install virtual evironment and flask
4. Navigate to your folder.
5. Execute the following commands
   env\Scripts\activate
   python app.py
6. Open browser and open the following website
   http://127.0.0.1:5000/
